  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of music to the postoperative pain and&#xD;
      discomfort after orbital decompression.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To investigate the effect of music to the postoperative pain and discomfort after orbital&#xD;
      decompression under general anesthesia.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
